{"tid":856164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一萬億可以買2500支SpaceX火箭","createTime":"2018-10-10T12:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T19:27:25.000Z","uid":38973,"like":172,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdf80adfbeb169573d98bb35333f7f4fce6a0fc","tid":856164,"uid":38973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"人哋用自己搵既20億都無既港紙 開咗自己既太空同電動車公司 一路做起上<br />\n香港人直程夾份送埋500億港紙比政府 出咗個八段錦就乜鳩都唔見喇<br />\n<br />\n人哋依家可以做到4億港紙幫人送貨上太空<br />\n香港人依家4億港紙可以起好一條天橋已經偷笑<br />\n<br />\n人哋用幾百億港紙去研發火箭 發展火星城市、開拓宇宙殖民地<br />\n香港人就用成萬幾億去係地球亞洲沿岸一個小城市整幾個人工島仔<br />\n<br />\n人哋期望研制完之後去火星機票價格可以降到去三百萬港紙 比你喺嗰度定居 研發費唔洗你埋單<br />\n香港人期望到填完海之後仲可以係人工島用三百萬港紙用成世供到間一百尺劏房養老 填海全香港埋單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">醒啦 盡你所能為香港去做返啲事啦各位</span>"},{"pid":"cec39eb191706ea2773e5839cfbb7f29bdd969e6","tid":856164,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65529becd8dc4920050c674ce72fef9d5d3a431","tid":856164,"uid":38973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c445031d7dc7008da68d93a90dd543094e2a50c7","tid":856164,"uid":142067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c970cdf6e6337cce0242c5a4049f3ddd5f1ea2","tid":856164,"uid":55602,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"買起musk所有公司都得添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7020b7991e1cc4649610cb